:"one","s":139.26,"e":139.54,"line":18},{"w":"chair","s":139.54,"e":140.22,"line":18},{"w":"one","s":140.26,"e":141.2,"line":18},{"w":"prayer","s":141.2,"e":141.88,"line":18},{"w":"Still","s":143.36,"e":144.72,"line":19},{"w":"here","s":144.72,"e":145.38,"line":19}],"lines":[{"s":2.22,"e":10.84,"text":"I was lucky I walked in When my roll got thin"},{"s":11.64,"e":18.88,"text":"Coffee in a paper cup Truth under my skin"},{"s":20.68,"e":27.9,"text":"Alcoholics anonymous, miracle in chairs Strangers telling stories like somebody cares"},{"s":27.9,"e":34.18,"text":"No velvet rope, no perfect face Just broken people finding grace"},{"s":34.18,"e":41.16,"text":"I heard keep coming hurt, take it slow Heard old pain, finally let go"},{"s":41.16,"e":47.86,"text":"Not magic like a trick in the air But spirit moving through the prayer"},{"s":47.86,"e":53.22,"text":"In the rooms with the light on I learned I wasn't alone"},{"s":54.76,"e":63.38,"text":"One day, one breath, one hand to hold A humble heart can still come home"},{"s":65.54,"e":76.38,"text":"A miracle when the soul gets honest Spiritual fire and a simple promise"},{"s":76.38,"e":80.28,"text":"Nobody flexing, nobody crowned This truth in a bottle tried to drag us down"},{"s":80.28,"e":83.78,"text":"Higher power, open door Knees on the ground but hope on the floor"},{"s":83.78,"e":87.36,"text":"I was lucky that I got to see People become who they're meant to be"},{"s":87.36,"e":91.98,"text":"Not by ego, not by pride But by letting something greater inside"},{"s":92,"e":95.8,"text":"Tell the truth, make it right Call somebody late at night"},{"s":95.8,"e":103.14,"text":"Clean the wreckage, lose the shame Help the next one do the same"},{"s":103.14,"e":109.98,"text":"In the rooms with the light on I learned I wasn't alone"},{"s":111.2,"e":118.84,"text":"One day, one breath, one hand to hold A humble heart can still come home"},{"s":121.86,"e":132.82,"text":"A miracle when the soul gets honest Spiritual fire and a simple promise"},{"s":132.82,"e":141.62,"text":"One day at a time One room, one chair, one prayer"},{"s":143.36,"e":145.38,"text":"Still here"}],"duration":146.47999572753906,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:32:18.996Z","model":"whisper-1"}